snippet.textDisplay: i almost went on a trip to mexico to see my fam right before we got the lock down order. i almost got stuck with my fam. but we decided it would be better to stay. if we just decided to go and deal with the consequences, i would be surrounded by my awesome family, which would have been the best thing to have happened to me in this situation. i love my family.
